file.name: api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Transforms
  version: v1beta1
  description: |
    Fawkes Transforms REST API.
    Transforms information and some calculations.
  contact:
    name:  Tim Niemueller
    email: niemueller@kbsg.rwth-aachen.de
  license:
    name: Apache 2.0
    url: 'http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html'

tags:
  - name: public
    description: Transforms public API.

paths:
  /transforms/graph:
    get:
      tags:
      - public
      summary: Get transform graph.
      operationId: get_graph
      description: |
        Get a a dot graph representation of the transforms.
      parameters:
        - name: pretty
          in: query
          description: Request pretty printed reply.
          allowEmptyValue: true
          schema:
            type: boolean
      responses:
        '200':
          description: get transform graph
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/TransformsGraph'
        '503':
          description: frames cannot be retrieved

components:
  schemas:
    TransformsGraph:
      type: object
      required:
        - kind
        - apiVersion
        - dotgraph
      properties:
        kind:
          type: string
        apiVersion:
          type: string
        dotgraph:
          type: string
